transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra, how can I assist you?

Speaker 2: Hi, yes, my name is Carlos Pulido and I talked to someone, I think it was last Thursday or Friday about my order being wrong, that they sent me sildenafil instead of the stuff that I ordered and they said, I mean supposedly I was going to get the ATV stuff and I only got the regular sildenafil which I used to get from my local pharmacy and way cheaper than what I paid and I never got the ATV and he said that he was going to send the correct dosage and now it's last Thursday and I haven't received an email confirming that it's been delivered, I want to know what the status is.

Speaker 1: What's your date of birth?

Speaker 2: April 27, 1962.

Speaker 1: Thank you.

Speaker 2: Okay, it looks like your order was shipped, the replacement order that they sent out and it looks like the expected delivery date is Tuesday the 17th.

Speaker 1: Next week?

Speaker 2: Yeah, next week Tuesday.

Speaker 1: Through what?

Speaker 2: Through the regular US mail?

Speaker 1: Yeah, the regular post office.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: Well, thank you.

Speaker 2: You're welcome, enjoy the rest of your day.
